# Documentation Update Policy

- **Always update nearest docs after successful changes**:
  - `CHANGELOG.md`: Summarize edits, scope, and impact near the changed files
  - `README.md`: Update high-level behavior; include CST/CDT last-updated timestamp
  - `STRUCTURE.md`: Reflect structure changes
- Prefer concise, high-signal notes. Reference files with backticks.
